<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM10.6">
<l>taṉamaruvu vaitēki piriya luṟṟut taḷarveytic caṭāyuvaivai kuntat tēṟṟi</l>
<l>vaṉamaruvu kaviyaracaṉ kātal koṇṭu vāliyaikkoṉ ṟilaṅkainaka rarakkar kōmāṉ</l>
<l>ciṉamaṭaṅka mārutiyāṟ cuṭuvit tāṉait tillainakart tiruccitra kūṭan taṉṉuḷ</l>
<l>ḷiṉitamarnta vammāṉai yirāmaṉ ṟaṉṉai yēttuvā riṇaiyaṭiyē yētti ṉēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have praised the pair of feet of those who praise</l>
<l rend="indent">Rāma, the Lord who is sweetly seated inside Tiruccitrakūṭam in the town of Tillai,</l>
<l rend="indent">who suffered separation from Vaidehī in whom wealth abides,</l>
<l rend="indent">lifted up Jaṭāyu to Vaikuṇṭha,</l>
<l rend="indent">felt affection for the king of the apes dwelling in the forest,</l>
<l rend="indent">killed Vālin</l>
<l rend="indent">and had the city of Laṅkā burnt through Māruti</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the anger of the emperor of the rakshasas was subdued.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
